            <title>[LU-13509] Improve ptlrpc_register_bulk() behavior</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13509</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The fix for &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/36309&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/36309&lt;/a&gt; could be improved a bit. It makes more sense to clear the bd_registered flag in ptlrpc_unregister_bulk() since it is set in ptlrpc_register_bulk().&lt;/p&gt;

